    "description": {
      "value": "<p>The Fire breath weapon can be formed into a Line 30 ft. long, 5 feet high, and 5 feet wide or into a Cone 15 ft. long. The character's breath weapon is able to affect a larger area as he progresses. The distance increases by 5 ft. per 2 HD of the Keeper beyond 4. The attack deals 3d6 damage to each creature in the cone or the first creature hit in a line attack and deals fire damage up to 11d6.</p>\n\n<hr><p><b>Requires:</b> Advanced Bloodline Flame Keeper (f)</p>\n<p><b>Empower:</b> The user may spend 1 point of chakra to increase the damage by 1 die, maximum 1 die per level</p>\n",
